### List conversations - should return 200 OK with paginated list of conversations
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/conversations?page=0&size=5   

### Sorted by createdAt desc - should return newest conversations first with pagination
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/conversations?page=0&size=5&sort=createdAt,desc

### Sorted by createdAt asc - should return oldest conversations first
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/conversations?sort=createdAt,asc&size=5

### Create conversation - should return 201 Created with Location header and response body                                                                                                  
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/conversations
Content-Type: application/json

{                                                                                                                                                
"title": "Test",
"source": "manual",
"rawContent": "Some content here"
}    

### Validation FAILURE - missing title - should be 400 Bad Request
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/conversations
Content-Type: application/json

{
"source": "manual",
"rawContent": "Some content here"
}

### Validation FAILURE - missing rawContent - should be 400 Bad Request
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/conversations
Content-Type: application/json

{
"title": "Test",
"source": "manual"
}

### Validation FAILURE - Empty title - should be 400 Bad Request
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/conversations
Content-Type: application/json

{
"title": "",
"source": "manual",
"rawContent": "Some content here"
}